---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 171
By: Sri Ramakrishna
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Volition, Obedience and Conformity=Intention
  - 965
---
The magnetic needle always points towards the north, ana hence it is
that the sailing vessel does not lose her course. So long as the heart
of man is directed towards God, he cannot be lost in the ocean of
worldliness.
